          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/64915142/" class=" " title="Manius">Manius</a>
                (拥塞败芝兰，众多盛荆杞)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="21798097">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/21798097/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p21798097-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 此，正是平治土地、修除水道、建造城郭的良机……龙潜北方，土功其始，该是主司水土的司空之官兴师动众、大兴土木的时候了</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/21798097/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-10-17 12:07</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p21798097-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>此，正是平治土地、修除水道、建造城郭的良机……龙潜北方，土功其始，该是主司水土的司空之官兴师动众、大兴土木的时候了
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







